{"tid":842571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳費sir 懼曼聯成英超笑柄","createTime":"2018-09-30T12:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:58:26.000Z","uid":37875,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5f9c97b260e071c9c01b81fdbbaf873201d5b1","tid":842571,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=fDVrsvPobmzEZ9WNWW4ClHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f224336c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】自領隊費格遜離開之後，英超豪門曼聯中興無期，更有傳爵爺非常擔心，怕曼聯將長久失去光芒。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯傳奇領隊費格遜（Sir Alex Ferguson）帶領「紅魔鬼」奪得13次英超冠軍，與曼聯情誼之深不容置疑。而看到球會近年來成績下滑，多次易帥仍未見起色，有傳費格遜與友人表示自己非常擔心，怕曼聯淪為「馬戲團球會」，成英超笑柄。<br />\n<br />\n除了爵爺之外，近日不少曼聯名宿都曾表達自己的不安，「92班」主將加利尼維利就認為球會一開始就已經「自毀長城」，沒有給予一眾領隊充裕時間去組軍，而里奧費迪南就表示：「單單球會的事並不是事情的全部，場內場外大小事情都是足球的一部分。現時的曼聯並未表現出成功球會的運作風格，尤其是你要保持球隊內的團結一致。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"16a1464c6215ff1f6f0628ca306958b2e2997476","tid":842571,"uid":70439,"like":84,"dislike":4,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"毋須擔心，因為已成笑柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0584439c4801f810e17f67df5d9157a5b272248","tid":842571,"uid":30768,"like":34,"dislike":5,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"笑咗幾年啦，費蛇病到失咗億牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442f2b3944f5df1a5092d80a665a0a2ad53f476a","tid":842571,"uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec79ac931e8ef60f56931a03c88affed3aa5ca4","tid":842571,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <